OL,3,CMother of teen murdered at house party
OL,4,Ctakes part in new documentary
OL,6,FThe mother of a teenager who was
OL,7,Ffatally stabbed at a house party in
OL,8,FBath has taken part in a new
OL,9,Fdocumentary exploring his murder and
OL,10,Fraising awareness about the realities
OL,11,Fof knife crime.
OL,13,FHayley Ryall's 16 year-old son, Mikey
OL,14,FRoynon was killed in June 2023 by a
OL,15,Fsingle stab wound to the neck with a
OL,16,Fzombie knife.
