OL,3,CMother of teen murdered at house party
OL,4,Ctakes part in new documentary
OL,6,FTeenager Shane Cunningham was
OL,7,Fconvicted of his murder after a trial
OL,8,Fat Bristol Crown Court. Neither boys
OL,9,Fwere known to each other before
OL,10,Fmeeting that night.
OL,12,FThe new documentary, House Party
OL,13,FKiller, is presented by Laura Whitmore
OL,14,Fand will air on Sky and Prime Video on
OL,15,FWednesday 14 January.
OL,17,FIt explores Mikey's childhood and his
OL,18,Finterests as he grows up, as well the
OL,19,Fevents that led to his death.
