OL,3,CMother of teen murdered at house party
OL,4,Ctakes part in new documentary
OL,6,FHayley said retelling the story was
OL,7,Fhard "but it tells the world about how
OL,8,FI feel, about what happened."
OL,10,F"It can happen to anybody. I never
OL,11,Fthought it could happen to us." she
OL,12,Fsaid, "Knife crime is everywhere, not
OL,13,Fjust in certain areas."
OL,15,FHayley believes raising awareness
OL,16,Fabout the dangers of knife crime is
OL,17,Fmaking a difference, with incidents
OL,18,Fcoming down in her local area.
