OL,3,CMother of teen murdered at house party
OL,4,Ctakes part in new documentary
OL,6,F"Which is a really positive move
OL,7,Fforward" she said. "Not anywhere near
OL,8,Fwhere we want it to be but it's come
OL,9,Fdown, so that's good."
OL,11,F"I think more parents are talking to
OL,12,Ftheir kids about it, there's much more
OL,13,Fon TV, but I think more can be done."
OL,15,FBeyond the documentary, Hayley plans
OL,16,Fto do more work on promoting
OL,17,Fpreventative measures when it comes to
OL,18,Fknife crime.
OL,20,F"The only reason I do all of this is
OL,21,Ffor him, for my boy."
